name: Water Horse
description: This Pokémon can escape from its opponents in a variety of ways.

attacks.name: Smokescreen
attacks.effect: Creates a cloud of black smoke. This is a move that the Pokémon learned by observing ninja.

name: Alola Raichu
description: This form only occurs in the Alola region. According to researchers, this adaptation is likely due to its diet.

attacks.name: Psychic
attacks.effect: Uses tarot cards to predict the future. Can also channel your dead grandma.

name: Balloon
description: There are stories of it grabbing young children by the hand and dragging them to the afterlife.

attacks.name: Selfdestruct
attacks.effect: An exploding bomb that can injure yourself or others. Editor's note: I'm afraid the balloon will pop.

name: Beaver
description: This Pokémon knows no fear. It is strong, fast, and cunning. Its daily routine is gnawing at logs.

attacks.name: Taunt
attacks.effect: To mentally and psychologically torment the opponent until they feel uncomfortable.

name: Pidgey
description: A common bird Pokémon. It dislikes conflict and often runs away from battle.

attacks.name: Sand-attack
attacks.effect: Kick sand into the opponent's eyes and run away. A truly cowardly move.

name: Ducky
description: Possesses powerful psychic abilities, but they only come into play when having a chronic headache.

attacks.name: Amnesia
attacks.effect: Forget everything that is happening right now. This somehow increases special defense. Editor's note: I do this all the time, but my special defense never goes up.

name: Mud Creef
description: Its strength is so great that it can destroy mountains with a single blow, and even legends dare not challenge this creature.

attacks.name: Punch
attacks.effect: Throws a punch at the opponent.

name: Light Boy
description: This Pokémon is very loyal to whomever suits it best.

attacks.name: Psychic
attacks.effect: An experimental move using psychic energy to cause the opponent to have an intense and unpleasant psychedelic experience. Also known as a bad trip.

name: Trumpety
description: Able to melt giant rocks with its fire breath.

attacks.name: Fire Blast
attacks.effect: A powerful flame that can deal a lot of damage. Can also be used to make s'mores.

name: Sukawai
description: Its exact appearance is unknown. A scholar who saw what was underneath the rag was overcome with fear and died of shock.

attacks.name: Copycat
attacks.effect: Copy the opponent.

name: Gau
description: This Pokémon has always been rare, and is believed to be the ancestor of all Pokémon.

attacks.name: Transform
attacks.effect: It can take on the exact same appearance as the opponent and use their techniques. If this is used on a doujin (same person), it will result in a long night.

name: Shanpe
description: If it senses danger it will immediately teleport away.

attacks.name: Teleport
attacks.effect: To instantly teleport to another location. Also known as teleportation.

name: Nugget
description: It has a flame inside that never goes out.

attacks.name: Flamethrower
attacks.effect: An extremely powerful flame attack. Only the most powerful and experienced Pokémon can pull off this move.

name: Meow
description: This creature is cute and fluffy, but highly intelligent and devious! I have a kind heart and like to spend my days sleeping.

attacks.name: Yawn
attacks.effect: I yawn and then I go to sleep. It's a cute trick, but it doesn't work.

attacks.name: Payday
attacks.effect: Attacks to make your opponent drop money.

name: Naruto
description: It can fly faster than any other Pokémon. It can circle the Earth in just 16 hours.

attacks.name: Dragon Dance
attacks.effect: The user performs a dance that increases their attack power and speed. The effect lasts for up to 30 minutes, requiring multiple costume changes.

name: Piccolo
description: The shell becomes as hard as iron.

attacks.name: Harden
attacks.effect: To become hard.

name: Egg Boy
description: This Pokémon is very rare. When encountered, it quickly runs away.

attacks.name: Softboiled
attacks.effect: Lay and eat boiled eggs. To be honest, it's very unpleasant.

name: Nidonido
description: This sign is very aggressive and rebellious. It even has a desire to protect its home.

attacks.name: Cut
attacks.effect: Cut whatever is in front of you.

name: Green Boy
description: This Pokémon is born with a seed on its back. They grow at the same rate and eventually become part of the body.

attacks.name: Leech Seed
attacks.effect: A terrifying attack that slowly sucks the life out of the opponent, eventually leaving them as a corpse.

name: Furphy
description: This creature is capable of solving difficult puzzles and has an extremely high IQ.

attacks.name: Stick Slap
attacks.effect: Hitting the opponent with a stick, leaving a lump on the opponent's head.

name: Hanbot
description: The water stream from the shell's rocket launcher has the destructive power to pierce even thick steel plates with a single shot.

attacks.name: Hydro Pump
attacks.effect: Shoots a powerful jet of water at the opponent. Also effective at cleaning cars and trucks.

name: Brown Rod
description: This Pokémon is very sensitive to sunlight. It spends almost its entire life underground.

attacks.name: Dig
attacks.effect: Dig a hole.

name: Gontar
description: It absorbs heat from anything around it. If you suddenly feel a chill, it's a sign that Gengar is nearby.

attacks.name: Curse
attacks.effect: This technique inflicts injustice on the opponent. This includes various types of bad luck, such as being hit by lightning or being stuck in traffic.

name: Shiny Fish
description: This Pokémon is nearly useless in battle, but it tastes delicious when roasted and seasoned with salt.

attacks.name: Splash
attacks.effect: In most cases, it does no damage. (Roll a d6 5 times. If the same number appears on all dice rolls, it's an instant KO.)

name: Pink Boy
description: The frequency of the singing voice perfectly match the brain waves of a person in deep sleep.

attacks.name: Sing
attacks.effect: It sings a variety of songs that are popular among young people today.

attacks.name: Doubleslap
attacks.effect: Slapping the opponent with its small pink hand.

name: Croco
description: This Pokémon has a very strong jaw.

attacks.name: Bite
attacks.effect: Biting the opponent.

attacks.name: Water Gun
attacks.effect: Take out the water gun you bought at the toy store and spray it at the opponent.

name: Eevee
description: This Pokémon is a big foodie. It only eats French fries and Hot Pockets.

attacks.name: Scratch
attacks.effect: It drags its opponents along with its long, clawed fingers.

attacks.name: Leech Seed
attacks.effect: A terrifying attack that slowly sucks the life out of the opponent, eventually leaving them as a corpse.

name: Turtle Chips
description: When it's dangerous, it stays in the shell.

attacks.name: Bubble
attacks.effect: Likes to blow bubbles. So cute!

attacks.name: Rapid Spin
attacks.effect: Spins in a circle. Also very cute.

name: Gegedu
description: This organism is actually just a rock, and has baffled scientists and biologists since its discovery.

attacks.name: Earthquake
attacks.effect: Shakes the ground and attacks the opponent. It can cause great damage to cities.

name: Togouchi
description: This creature can taste sound with its eyes.

attacks.name: Energy Ball
attacks.effect: When it touches other creatures, nothing happens.

name: Blissui
description: This creature loves to protect and heal others. Therefore, it will not be used in combat and will not carry on the fight.

attacks.name: Egg Bomb
attacks.effect: Throws explosive eggs at opponents. Make it green and explode.

name: Dark Boy
description: The light emitted from its ring can be dimmed to become completely invisible in the dark of night.

attacks.name: Confuse Ray
attacks.effect: This attack makes the opponent question reality. Forces them to ask deep philosophical questions, like which arm-rest in a movie theater is theirs.

name: Robot
description: The first Pokémon created by humans. A Pokémon that came into being after many years of scientific research and experimentation.

attacks.name: Tri Attack
attacks.effect: Shoots a beam made up of multiple elements.

name: Veronica
description: The day after it rains, the scent of flowers on its back intensifies. Pokémon gather there, drawn by the scent.

attacks.name: Solarbeam
attacks.effect: Attacks the opponent with energy collected from the sun. Also gives them Vitamin D and may cause a sunburn.

name: Boat
description: A peaceful Pokémon that is happy for you to be carried on its back.

attacks.name: Surf
attacks.effect: Skilled at surfing and impresses its friends with its skills.

name: Heavy Boy
description: Is able to levitate thanks to the magnetic field generated within its body.

attacks.name: Thunder Wave
attacks.effect: An attack that paralyzes the target with a wave of electricity.

name: Sleepy Boy
description: A fat, lazy, and always hungry Pokémon. It will eat anything, even if it's poisonous.

attacks.name: Rest
attacks.effect: Falls asleep. Snorlax is good at this move.

attacks.name: Snore
attacks.effect: Attacks while asleep.

name: Skipper
description: This Pokémon spends most of its time hiding in the mud.

attacks.name: Growl
attacks.effect: It growls at the opponent. It's meant to scare them, but it's also pretty cute.

attacks.name: Water Gun
attacks.effect: Spits water at the opponent.

name: Slow Mo
description: This creature uses a sixth sense to see into the future.

attacks.name: Hypnotist
attacks.effect: Uses telekinesis to enter the mind of his victim and tells him to do 50 embarrassing things in front of his friends.

name: Cutiepie
description: Items can be recharged when placed on the head.

attacks.name: Thunderpunch
attacks.effect: Uses electricity to punch the enemy. Since his arms are small, this attack often misses.

name: Wormy
description: This Pokémon was considered a legendary Pokémon until a small colony was discovered under water.

attacks.name: Dragon Tail
attacks.effect: Attacks the opponent with its tail.

attacks.name: Leer
attacks.effect: Stare at the opponent.

name: Lavatar
description: This Pokémon was born under a large mountain. It takes years to eat up all of its food, and after it does, it takes a long nap.

attacks.name: Rock Throw
attacks.effect: Picking up a rock and throwing it at the opponent. This was a technique often used in high school.

name: Kitty
description: Hates the affection from people it trusts. Twice a year, sets itself on fire to burn off the old fur.

attacks.name: Double Kick
attacks.effect: This skill is difficult to master. The opponent is beaten not just once, but twice.

name: Pidgeotto
description: This creature was once abundant on Earth, but now only a handful remain.

attacks.name: Stomp
attacks.effect: Trample and forcefully attack your opponent.

name: Buggy
description: A Pokémon that spends all day collecting nectar from flowers.

attacks.name: Poisonpowder
attacks.effect: Causes a poison status on the opponent.

attacks.name: Stun Spore
attacks.effect: Paralyze the opponent.

name: Dakarei
description: A Pokémon created in a laboratory through gene splicing. It has a body suited for battle, but lacks a compassionate heart.

attacks.name: Future Sight
attacks.effect: Attacks the opponent in the future with psychic powers. Pray that it's not when you're on the toilet.

name: Are You Who
description: It is said to have emerged from an egg in the middle of nowhere and created the world.

attacks.name: Judgment
attacks.effect: Arceus looks at you with judgment. As a god, it knows all your weirdness.

name: Nidanida
description: This creature has magical powers that can be used to contact its body.

attacks.name: Tummy Kick
attacks.effect: Kicks the opponent in the stomach, causing hours of pain.

name: Wamp
description: This Pokémon spends its time eating leaves and running away from Starlys.

attacks.name: String Shot
attacks.effect: Shoots silk threads around the opponent, lowering their speed.

name: Firefox
description: This Pokémon is born with one tail, which divides into six as it grows up.

attacks.name: Will-o-wisp
attacks.effect: Attacks the opponent and burns them.

attacks.name: Grudge
attacks.effect: It's resentful of the person who didn't send a happy birthday email.

name: Motherless Boy
description: Wears the skull of its deceased mother. It's said to evolve when enduring the pain of the mother's death.

attacks.name: Bone Rush
attacks.effect: Rush towards the opponent and attack with bones.

name: Big Bat
description: They love to drink blood. Once they sink their teeth into their prey, they can instantly take up to 10 ounces or more of blood.

attacks.name: Screech
attacks.effect: It produces a very annoying noise.

name: Clompy
description: Pikachu is by far the most famous Pokémon. Its personality has changed with the games and attention it receives.

attacks.name: Shock
attacks.effect: Pikachu gives the opponent an electric shock as strong as a toaster.

name: Plant Boy
description: This Pokémon plants during the day and wakes up at dusk to roam and spread seeds.

attacks.name: Growth
attacks.effect: Its body grows. Who needs protein powder? This is natural.

name: Long Worm
description: A Pokémon that emits a mysterious aura. It can change the weather with its emotions.

attacks.name: Rain Dance
attacks.effect: Performs a dance that changes the weather.

attacks.name: Dragon Rush
attacks.effect: Charges at the opponent with dragon-like movements.

name: Pointy
description: Its claws can crush anything.

attacks.name: Swords Dance
attacks.effect: Dance with swords. Do not use at home.

attacks.name: Iron Head
attacks.effect: Attacks the opponent with its head.

name: Fire Boy
description: If the flame goes out, it dies.

attacks.name: Mean Look
attacks.effect: Disrespecting the opponent.

attacks.name: Ember
attacks.effect: Weak fire attack.

name: Egg Bath
description: A Pokémon that seals happiness in its shell and gives it to people. It is said that it brings good luck.

attacks.name: Yawn
attacks.effect: When it yawns, the opponent will yawn too.

name: Blob
description: Not only can it take on the appearance and skills of other Pokémon, but you can also mate and breed with other Pokémon. Many trainers use them for breeding purposes.

attacks.name: Transform
attacks.effect: Transform into the opponent.

name: Ghost Boy
description: A Pokémon made mostly of gas.

attacks.name: Lick
attacks.effect: Lick the opponent. Some Pokémon enjoy this, so be careful.

name: Siechacha
description: This creature loves to fight, and will take on anything while spending its entire life communicating.

attacks.name: Hyper Cut
attacks.effect: Slice the opponent into pieces with a devastating blow.

attacks.name: Bug's Gaze
attacks.effect: Stare at the opponent, causing extreme discomfort.

name: Ghost Boy
description: They are extremely mischievous creatures, and their daily routine is to scare and play pranks on others.

attacks.name: Scare
attacks.effect: Deform its body and face to scare the opponent. This reduces the opponent's attack power.

name: Bonzie
description: Known for burying its lower body in the ground as a defense, and will continue in this state until it's strong enough to defend itself properly.

attacks.name: Kick
attacks.effect: Kicks the opponent with the small leg. It's not very effective.
